Package de.stocker.persistence

Class OpenFrame

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.stocker.persistence.OpenFrame
  • class OpenFrame
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class OpenFrame is used for collecting information about all open internal frames displayed in the application main frame. This information is used to store the state of the application on a file on disk and to restore it after a restart.
    Author:
    Matthias Rudolph
